<br>
thanks <p><b>Bomban Weesecksy</b> <br>55 Myrmidon <br>Rallos Zek <br>Fire Beetles
<img src=http://www.geocities.com/bombanrz/sig1.jpg align=center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/urivenwry.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rivenwry</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/19/01 7:27:19 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Enchanter battles</span><hr size=1> Be realistic peoples...<br>
<br>
The last BOB group showed that actual groups were the best for the thing, not all monks or rogue or whatever<br>
<br>
Rivenwry <p>I know what you're doing...
I see it all, too clear.</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uwiergraf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Wiergraf</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_lightning.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/21/01 4:08:10 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Enchanter battles</span><hr size=1> Okay Bomban, about rogue poison.<br>
<br>
As far as I know, the DoTs and root uses of poison can be cured via pumice stone or whatever, but blindness and DDs cannot.<br>
<br>
And it can also be resisted, but since it is resisted by using yer Poison resistance, the only time my poisons have been resisted against something even close to an even con was against a necro with Dead Man Floating. <p><br>
